actions.text: Reported to Senate from the Committee on Rules and Administration, S. Rept. 93-1290.

official_title: Resolution reported from the committee on Rules and Administration authorizing additional expenditures.

summary.text: Authorizes the Senate Committee on Rules and Administration to expend from the contingent fund of the Senate, during the Ninety-third Congress, $30,000 in addition to the amount, and for the same purpose, specified in the Legislative Reorganization Act of 1946 and in S. Res. 317 of the Ninety-third Congress.

titles.title: Resolution reported from the committee on Rules and Administration authorizing additional expenditures.
